201
00:13:25.175 --> 00:13:27.875
Itu tidak penting.

202
00:13:27.875 --> 00:13:32.375
Kita melihat saat dia jatuh.

203
00:13:32.375 --> 00:13:33.975
Benar, bukan?

204
00:13:33.975 --> 00:13:34.975
Ya.

205
00:13:36.775 --> 00:13:40.775
